verbose_text: As evidenced by MTT assay, use of an SEM, calcein-AM/PI staining, H & E staining, Safranin O staining, IHC and RT-qPCR, cell growth and cartilage specific ECM components, including AGC and COL1A2, were promoted in the nHC film compared with that in the control.
